@startuml
left to right direction
skinparam componentStyle rectangle

title market-mvp, Component Diagram

package "Client Layer" {
  [React UI] as UI
}

package "Facade Layer" {
  [BFF] as BFF
}

package "Domain / Source Services" {
  [ClientService] as ClientService
  [PortfolioService] as PortfolioService
  [InstrumentService] as InstrumentService
}

package "Streaming / Projection" {
  [MarketDataIngestor] as Ingestor
  [PriceProjectionService] as PriceProjection
  [PortfolioValuationService] as Valuation
  queue "Kafka\nmarket.price-ticks" as Kafka
  database "Redis\nprice / valuation / summary" as Redis
}

package "Observability" {
  [Kafka UI] as KafkaUI
}

UI --> BFF : UI DTO requests
BFF --> ClientService : clients
BFF --> PortfolioService : accounts
BFF --> Valuation : summaries / valuations
BFF --> InstrumentService : instrument details

Ingestor --> Kafka : publish ticks
Kafka --> PriceProjection : consume ticks
PriceProjection --> Redis : current prices
Valuation --> PortfolioService : positions
Valuation --> InstrumentService : instruments
Valuation --> PriceProjection : prices API
Valuation --> Redis : valuation snapshots
Valuation --> Redis : account summaries

KafkaUI --> Kafka : inspect topic/groups
UI ..> Redis : does not access directly
BFF ..> Redis : does not access directly

note right of BFF
BFF не владеет бизнес-данными.
Он фасад для UI.
end note

note bottom of Redis
Redis хранит hot read state,
а не source of truth.
end note

@enduml
